column5:
36 pages, 19 figures; an error in Section 4.3 was corrected (main
  result unchanged); a corresponding example with a figure was added;
  explanations and a reference to the example were added to the introduction;
  in particular, Definition 1.3 of the relative Morse boundary was improved;
  pictures were improved; typos corrected; a remark in section 6 was added
